1.0 StructureDefinition-Phenopacket

1.0.1 Formal Views of Profile Content

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://ga4gh.org/fhir/phenopackets/StructureDefinition/Phenopacket

A Phenopacket is an anonymous phenotypic description of an individual or biosample with potential genes of interest and/or diagnoses.

This profile builds on Composition.

This profile was published on Mon Dec 02 08:48:39 AEST 2019 as a draft by Global Alliance for Genomics and Health.

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots, and how the XML and JSON presentations work.
